Package: suacir
Title: Access SUACI Open Data from Buenos Aires
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Juan Pablo", "Ripamonti", email = "juan.ripamonti@phd.unibocconi.it",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Download and analyze data from the Sistema Unico de Atencion
    Ciudadana (SUACI), published by the Buenos Aires City Government on the
    Buenos Aires Data portal <https://data.buenosaires.gob.ar>. Provides
    functions to retrieve data for individual years or the full historical
    series, with consistent column names and types across all available years.
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/jpripamonti/suacir
BugReports: https://github.com/jpripamonti/suacir/issues
